Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive

Epidemiological comments: Vector control measures have been strengthened. Surveillance of wild ruminants has been strengthened, and no cases have been detected.

Control measures at event level
Control measures applied, domestic: control of vectors, surveillance outside containment and/or protection zone, surveillance within containment and/or protection zone, vector surveillance

Control measures applied, wild: surveillance outside containment and/or protection zone, surveillance within containment and/or protection zone

